    <h1 class="w3-center w3-text-grey"><b>Destruction of the ozone layer.</b></h1>
    <img class="w3-round" src="https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcT5CF0JUoNI8G5iuhaA5n0a-Y9kD5Fy2ZaFNCBMs2a5BtN8HiLK" style="width:100%;margin:32px 0">
    <p><i>We come up with a solution of an animation. An animation that contains the facts and informations. Such as giving our participants the cause and effects of our topic which is Depletion Of Ozone Layer. And stating to them, who are involved, what are the things that they are doing that cause the risk behavior. And on how they can stop the risk behavior that they are doing. We choose the animation as our solution, because it's the easiest way to explain our topic to our participants.</i></p>
    <h3> CAUSES OF THE PROBLEM</h3>
    <p>Cause #1 Chloroflouro Carbon<br>Cause #2 Vehicle emiting smoke<br>Cause #3 Volcanic Eruption<br></p>
    <h3> Usability Test</h3>
    <p>Question #1 Do you have any idea about ozone layer?<br>Question #2 Do you agree that it's getting hotter here in Earth? Why, or why not?<br>Question #3 Do you know waht are the possible reasons of why our ozone layer is getting depleted?<br>Question #4 Do you believe that the ozone layer is depleting because of human activities? If so, why?<br>Question #5 What are the possible solutions to refrain the ozone layer from getting depleted? List down the possible solution/s.<br>Question #6 what part of the video/animation are you infavor of?<br>Question #7 What part of our animation needs an improvement?<br>Question #8 What part of the solution do you like the most?<br>Question #9 What did you learn from our animation? State your answer.<br>Question #10 Do you think the information are enough to deliver the necessary message of the animation?</p>
    <p class="w3-center"><a href="#wedding" class="w3-button w3-yellow w3-round w3-padding-large w3-large">Solution</a></p>
  </div>
</div>

